marketing: Shell Marine Hydraulic Fluid MX fluids are high performance hydraulic fluids based on Group II base oils that provide outstanding protection and performance in many marine equipment operations. They resist breakdown under heat or mechanical stress and help prevent damaging deposit formation that can decrease the efficiency of your hydraulic power system.
